lead_paragraph: Venus Williams made a successful return yesterday after missing almost three months with an injured wrist when she defeated sixth-seeded Ana Ivanovic, 6-3 6-4, in the first round of the Luxembourg Championship. Williams, playing her first match since Wimbledon, won the match in 71 minutes.
